#: ../../source/recipes/swagger.rst:7
msgid ""
"The `OpenAPI <https://swagger.io/specification/>`__ (Swagger) "
"specification is a powerful definition format to describe RESTful APIs. "
"Nest provides a dedicated `module <https://github.com/nestjs/swagger>`__ "
"to work with it."
msgstr ""

