msgid ""
"warning **Notice** You have to construct a **SwaggerOptions** with "
"``DocumentBuilder``, run ``createDocument()`` against newly constructed "
"``options`` then immediately “serve” it with ``setup()`` before you can "
"start working on a second **SwaggerOptions** for a second Swagger "
"Specification. This specific order is to prevent Swagger configurations "
"being overridden by different options."
msgstr ""

